
Overview of noun hop

The noun hop has 3 senses (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                            
1. (1) hop -- (the act of hopping; jumping upward or forward (especially on one foot))
2. hop, hops -- (twining perennials having cordate leaves and flowers arranged in conelike spikes; the dried flowers of this plant are used in brewing to add the characteristic bitter taste to beer)
3. hop, record hop -- (an informal dance where popular music is played)

